author: johnh
msg: Implements Uri.resolve(...) natively instead of in terms of java.net.URI.
In addition to being a performance improvement (40%+), this allows UriParser-parsed Uris that don't conform to java.net.URI's restrictions
(eg. chars like | or ^) to resolve appropriately.
